Doke-Purpose: Load and validate the Doke runtime config passed by DokeBrowser.
Doke-Subsystem: chrome/app startup command-line handling.
Doke-Detection-Target: DokeBrowser profile.start, Doke/runtime.json, and tools/doke_runtime_check.py.
Doke-Rollback: Remove this patch from patches/chromium/series and rebuild Chromium; DokeBrowser will still pass --doke-runtime-config but Chromium will ignore it.

